{"tid":2255193,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫管局：暫未就政治清算程序作結論 感謝反共派在抗疫期間的努力","createTime":"2020-10-23T10:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T16:06:08.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"68f2334c14be8fd17156c103fc0bc409aef5ae3a","tid":2255193,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T10:54:19.000Z","msg":"醫管局：暫未就員工缺勤理由及跟進程序作結論<br />\n<br />\n醫管局表示，日前就部分員工在2月初缺勤的事宜向有關員工發信，請他們確認信內的缺勤日期是否正確，及向他們了解缺勤的原因，局方目前正在整理有關回覆，暫時未就回覆數目、員工所提供的缺勤理由及日後可能進行的跟進程序作結論。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，局方會按照法律意見及相關人事條例，以合情、合理和合法的方式公平處理，並會透過不同平台繼續與員工溝通。<br />\n<br />\n發言人重申，感謝員工在抗疫期間盡力照顧病人，期望繼續與所有員工共同應對公營醫療服務未來的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556373-20201023.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556373-20201023.htm&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=a2cab3f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556373-20201023.htm&h=65d89bad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556373-20201023.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e4d648acc71ca7710f523ba081931bb86eba00b6","tid":2255193,"uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T10:56:46.000Z","msg":"反共派？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根據國安法，反共已經拉得，問題係邊一樣係反共？"},{"pid":"866c44b4d02a81975d4c5e6195aaee3150acc805","tid":2255193,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:36:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448b8dd673ab3af7e32cc30429a546d9f4dd45b9","tid":2255193,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46324dfb04f7b197f219fda6383465307e44b93","tid":2255193,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:47:45.000Z","msg":"事實證明醫護有遠見有專業評估<br />\n<br />\n港共仲要攪醫護痴撚線"},{"pid":"833d19913d83853112ef6a9766a6167a5ced2010","tid":2255193,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T15:53:13.000Z","msg":"用bno去德國醫護人員好過 但要學好德文"},{"pid":"b4d133584ed168aedc78a7e4adbb1daa0b7f3dfa","tid":2255193,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"833d19913d83853112ef6a9766a6167a5ced2010","tid":2255193,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T15:53:13.000Z","msg":"用bno去德國醫護人員好過 但要學好德文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T15:53:38.000Z","msg":"用bno去德國做醫護人員好過 但要學好德文"},{"pid":"b0cbcae93e98b90438ec16b872fc8837404e9c89","tid":2255193,"uid":54623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T16:06:08.000Z","msg":"一路幫開香港既澳洲手足Drew Pavlou眾籌緊,仲差3000usd.請大家幫手<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/drew-pavlou-uq-fighting-fund\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fdrew-pavlou-uq-fighting-fund&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=12b12ee0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/drew-pavlou-uq-fighting-fund</a>"}]}